Recharge and unwind in this gorgeous space nestled in the woods. The Mountain Terrace has an indoor wood stove, a deck with a beautiful view, a fire-pit, 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. This stunning house has been recently renovated and offers total privacy and serenity - sitting on 5 acres at the end of a quiet road. There is a washer/dryer, a dishwasher an artist cabin and a yoga studio. An easy 15 min drive to Livingstone Manor for great restaurants, shopping and activities. Pet friendly.

The space
This stunning modern home has an open floor plan. The kitchen opens up to the living room and dining room. The home has two living rooms - one downstairs with the wood stove and one upstairs with the TV. There is also a nook for the perfect work-from-home spot as well as the terrace with jaw-dropping views. There are 3 bedrooms: one with a king sized bed, and two with queen sized beds. There are 2 bathrooms, one with a tub.

Guest access
The entire home and property is all yours. The home sits on the end of a quiet, private road and you have 5 acres all to yourselves. This includes the firepit with wood provided, the yoga studio, an artist shed, the house and all the surrounding land.

Other things to note
The Mountain Terrace sits on a secluded plot of land at the end of a half mile unpaved road. In the winter the road is plowed but needs a 4WD car to drive comfortably on the road.
